title: FRENS for other activities
body:
The proposal is to create new activities for FRENS usage, e.g. :
1) FRENS staking or\and add liquidity to GHST
2) FRENS pool (add FRENS to pool to gain GHST)
3) FRENS for FRIENDS (Referral program)
choices: No way, raffle's and that's all!
author: 0x8aa4B092f444767f483E573abAe6c0513D3dc839
